Notice.title: Study Tour
Notice.content:
Dear Students, 
Assalamualykum you will be happy to know that An entertainment tour is planned from our Ucchas Coaching Center. Our honorable chairman sir also gives his final decision yesterday and He order Managing director to give this notice to all. We decided to went Cox's bazaar sea beach. Coaching Center will bear all the expenses.  
Coaching center will provided this facilities 
1. Business class Bus
2. 5 star hotel [ jhol Torongo]
3. Breakfast , lunch , dinner 
Without that Coaching are not provided any others facilities. Tour will be held at June 1st week. 

Thank you
Managing Director 
Ucchas Coaching Center
